        <mattext texttype="text/html">&lt;h1&gt;Session 20 Quiz – Polish, Testing, and Deployment&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Test your understanding of error handling, testing, validation, and deployment best practices.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Topics Covered:&lt;/strong&gt;
- Error handling and try/catch
- Input validation
- Testing with console.assert
- Edge case handling
- Deployment configuration&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Instructions:&lt;/strong&gt;
- 16 questions from the Session 20 question bank
- 20 minute time limit
- 3 attempts allowed
- 16 points total (1 point per question)&lt;/p&gt;
